review:
Considering Speaker Size, Sound is really good and no need of extra speakers or soundbar at all; highly underated sound quality; Sound is better than what you expect after reading reviews;
Picture Quality is Great in Day time; super bright display, great upscaling of low resolution; this is the best part of tv; even SD content appear very good here;
Picture Quality in low light is not upto the mark; May be due to No micro dimming; But its bearable and not the reason to avoid this TV;
One major issue i noticed is little Screen backlight bleeding in white back ground and some dark patches appear in white background but while watching content its all good and no bleeding or patches appear;

will claim warranty if this issue worsen in due coruse;
